Saffron Sales Analysis & Forecasting Project:-

This project analyzes saffron sales data using Python, Pandas, Matplotlib, and basic forecasting techniques.
It explores revenue trends, customer segments, regional performance, and product-wise sales.
The goal is to identify insights that support inventory planning and business decision-making.

