Project Highlights:-

Sales Trend Analysis:
Monthly revenue trends
Seasonal peaks during festival & wedding months

Product Revenue Breakdown:
Comparison of revenue from different saffron product types

Regional Sales Insights:
Best-performing regions
Customer distribution patterns

Customer Segmentation:
Retail vs Wholesale contribution
Revenue share by customer type

Forecasting:
Simple forecasting using time-series trends
Helps plan inventory & marketing

Actionable Recommendations:
Stock planning
